title: Grass-Fed Beef Box Order ships & arrives separately. | 16 Servings
description: Skip the butcher counter lines—our friends at GoodChop deliver high-quality, hormone and antibiotic-free meat and seafood right to your door. Add this special box packed with four 100% grass-fed beef selections to your HelloFresh order to fortify your weekly meals, or just to have on hand. In this box, you’ll receive filet mignon (12 ounces), ground beef (2 pounds), bavette steaks (24 ounces), and ranch steaks (16 ounces). The best part? All of GoodChop’s products are responsibly raised and sustainably sourced right here in the USA!

*Your order will ship separately in a Good Chop-branded box and may not arrive on your scheduled weekly HF delivery date (shipping is included in the total price). Customization of bundles is not available at this time.
